My vim configuration.

HOW INSTALL:

ln -s vim-stuff/ .vim
ln -s vim-stuff/vimrc .vimrc

THEN:

cd .vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

INSTALLING BUNDLES:

git submodule add [git repository] bundle/[bundle dir]

ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENTS:

Must have Powerline patched fonts for vim-airline status bar plugin
https://github.com/Lokaltog/powerline-fonts. Then follow the instructions
from that repository in order to install those fonts.
